 to agar YAA QAADE-RO ka vird kare to bohot faaiyde mand hai.", "UrduDescription": "سلوک کے راستوں پر چلنے والا جب ہموم و وسوسہ میں مبتلا ہونے کا خوف محسوس کرے تو اگر ’’یَا قَادِرُ‘‘ کا ورد کرے تو بہت فائدہ مند ہے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1021336, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 4, "EnglishDescription": "One who is in control of his inner self (nafs’e ammarah) and whispering of shaitan has overpowered him, then if he recites this zikr for 40 days from dawn (saher) till namaz’e subh and after namaz’e subh till sunrise as much as he can, so then his inner self (nafs) will get so much strength and power that he will over power shaitan and he will be aware of surprising secrets…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Jo shakhs nafs ammaarah ki giraft mein ho aur waswase shaitaani us par ghaalib aa chuke ho to agar woh 40 din tak is zikr ka vird kare tuloo’e subh (1st twilight when the roza starts) se namaz’e subh (2nd twilight when the azaan’e subh starts) tak aur namaz’e subh ke baad se tuloo’e aaftaab (sunrise) tak jis qadar ziyadah se ziyadah ho sakey vird kare to us ke nafs mein itni quwwat o qudrat paiyda ho jaayegi keh woh shaitaan par ghaalib aa jaayega aur us par ajeeb o ghareeb usraar (raaz) zaahir hone lagenge…", "UrduDescription": "جو شخص نفس امارہ کی گرفت میں ہو اور وسوسہ شیطانی اس پر غالب آچکے ہوں تو اگر وہ 40 دن تک طلوع صبح سے نماز صبح تک اور نماز صبح کے بعد طلوع آفتاب تک جس قد رزیادہ سے زیادہ ہو سکے اس ذکر کا ورد کرے تو اس کے نفس میں اتنی قوت و قدرت پیدا ہوجائے گی کہ وہ شیطان پر غالب آجائے گا اور اس پر عجیب و غریب اسرار ظاہر ہونے لگیں گے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null,